
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Order Successful - YemekSiparis.Web</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            color: #495057;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .success-icon {
            font-size: 100px;
            color: #28a745;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #c9302c;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container text-center">
        <div class="success-icon animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">&#10004;</div>
        <h1 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">Siparişiniz Başarıyla Tamamlandı!</h1>
        <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">Siparişiniz alındı. Teşekkür ederiz!</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">Ana Sayfa'ya Dön</a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
